  -RESIZE AND MOVE FLOAT WINDOW WITHOUT MOUSE (WIN+SHIFT+M = FLOAT WINDOW)
    WIN+ALT+[hjkl]

  -RESIZE WIBOX WITH SINGLE MOUSE CLICK

  -HIDDEN/SHOW WINDOW BORDER COLOR (WIN+SHIFT+T) 

  -CHANGE RANDOM WALLPAPER (LEFT MOUSE CLICK ON DESKTOP)
  -REMEMBER LAST WALLPAPER (see bash/setWallpaper.sh)

